Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.02,Main,,0,0,0,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:05.65,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,It's open. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:08.15,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Mr. Rohan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:09.07,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Where are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:10.86,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,I'm here, Koichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:13.86,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Mr. Rohan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.86,0:00:18.28,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,What's wrong?\N You didn't really explain much over the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:20.45,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,I'm in need of your assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:22.50,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,I'm under attack by an enemy Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:23.29,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:26.88,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,A-A Stand? Where is it? Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:30.05,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,On my back. My back has been possessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:31.59,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:37.43,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Umm... Your back is being attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:42.27,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Precisely. This Stand is {\i1}extremely{\i0} dangerous!\N I'm at a loss for what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:44.19,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Can you show it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:45.10,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:48.27,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,But if you don't show it to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:51.28,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,It will transfer over to you and kill me in the process if I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:53.49,Main,Cheap Trick,0,0,0,,Hurry up and burn 'em, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.57,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,You see? It's talking! This is it, Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:00:57.16,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:00.16,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Why are you hiding it from me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:03.45,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Did you call me over just to mess with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:04.71,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:07.42,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,I just told you I would die if I showed you my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:11.92,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It would be just like you \Nto mess with me like this, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:14.17,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I knew something was up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:16.43,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,You're wrong! I couldn't be more serious right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:17.97,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,There's a corpse upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:20.10,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Huh? A-A corpse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:24.06,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Uh... What are you doing, Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:26.56,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Climb over me and go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:29.98,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Please, go on ahead of me! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:32.98,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Jeez, what is with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:35.28,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Well? Now do you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:37.45,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:39.53,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:40.87,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Right here, Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:49.25,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Look, Koichi! This is Kinoto Masazo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:51.79,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,He had the life sucked from his decaying body,\N and now he's all dried up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:55.05,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wow, that's amazing! It's really convincing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:02:00.09,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,But this is a bad time to be \Nmessing around like this, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:05.06,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,The new Stand users created by \Nthat old man in the photo are still coming after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:09.23,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,You made me rush over here thinking you had been attacked or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:10.36,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:11.86,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Then this thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:15.44,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Anyway, stay safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:16.11,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:17.95,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:23.45,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,I purposely asked you first since I knew those shit stains Okuyasu and Josuke would never believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:27.08,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Please believe me! We're friends, aren't we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:29.50,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:35.30,Main,Cheap Trick,0,0,0,,Don't feel blue, 'kay? \N'Cause that's really gotta sting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:40.59,Main,Roha,0,0,0,,I, Kishibe Rohan, have never faced such humiliation in all my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:44.01,Main,Roha,0,0,0,,You little creep... You'll regret this!
Comment: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:44.06,Main,,0,0,0,,OPENING
